data.description: Welcome to your dream country home set on over an acre! This spacious four-bedroom, two-bathroom gem offers the perfect blend of comfort and rustic charm. Step inside to an open layout invites you in with warmth. The large den provides extra versatile space for your needs. Indulge in breathtaking mountain views from the expansive front porch, a perfect spot to relax and soak in the serene surroundings. Saddle up your horses and explore the nearby trails leading to the national forest- a rider's paradise right at your doorstep. Equipped with a 3 stall barn, turn out,  this property is a horse lover's haven. Private well,  RV enthusiasts will appreciate the parking spaces. Don't miss out on this unique opportunity to own your slice of country paradise!
